text: Werner J. Uebelmann (16 March 1921 - 1 March 2014) was a Swiss entrepreneur and writer. He last best known for his large collection of cactus. He was born in Aarau, Aargau. Uebelmann died on 1 March 2014 in Muri, Aargau.
